data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION TO SELL!!! MOTIVATED SELLER!! DON'T LOOK ANY FURTHER! Take advantage of this amazing opportunity to own a completely remodeled house with tile flooring, quartz countertops, luxury cristal backsplash, 3 car garage, metal roof 2020, 2,101sqft , Reverse osmosis system, and much more. Living in a rural setting expose you to all the wonderful things nature has to offer. However, this wonderful house offers you NOT only 2.27 acres of land, but at the same time, your are just minutes away from the city of Naples, shopping centers, highest rated schools, hospitals, and fire station. Definitely a MUST SEE.
